thread.title_full: AMR reviewed by The Princess Cut Hair Artistry

author: The Princess Cut Hair Artistry
title: The Princess Cut Hair Artistry
text:
AMR is my go to stockist for my hair supplies, I love that they offer zip pay AND afterpay, making last minute orders less worry!
They have SUPER fast delivery (even to me living quite far out) along with their same day dispatch!
Customer service always happy and polite and helpful xo
